， 邊個最好玩最驚 ？"},{"pid":"20a7f31ccdc1ef30c39a7fe591a237d20a9e7210","tid":1045172,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"原來係個雕像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}